headline: 2 of Wall Street’s Favorite Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Turn Down

headline: Hon Hai Tech Day 2025 Opens To Showcase Foxconn's Powerful Partnerships And Vertical Integration Strengths
summary: Accelerating its transformation into an AI-powered technology platform service company, Hon Hai Technology Group ("Foxconn") (TWSE: 2317) on Friday welcomed powerful partnerships, including NVIDIA, OpenAI and Alphabet, and shared its unrivalled strength in vertical integration at its annual flagship technology conference, Hon Hai Tech Day 2025.

headline: Foxconn can make 1,000 AI racks a week, to increase next year, chairman says
summary: TAIPEI (Reuters) -Foxconn Chairman Young Liu said on Friday the company now had the capability to manufacture ​1,000 artificial intelligence racks per week, and it expected that rate ‌to increase next year.  Liu made the comments at the contract electronics manufacturer's tech day, which ‌was attended by Foxconn's partners and clients including Nvidia and OpenAI.  Foxconn's founder, Terry Gou, also made an appearance.

headline: Does Nvidia Stock Still Have Enough Mojo to Buy?
